{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs24 Non-Combat Skills in Combat\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 This table can be used to represent Skills which aren\u8217't normally intended for a fight (i.e., not Defense, Dueling, Aim, or Brawl) but which end up being used anyway. For example, a Mechanician might attempt to overload one of her devices or a Virtuosa could sing loud enough to shatter glass.\par}
