{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b Make a Connection:} You go out in public and are seen are by one reputable person who will unwittingly vouch for your identity. Each additional success point gives you another person who thinks you\u8217're who you\u8217're pretending to be.\par}
