{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b Prepare Rations (1 unit of foodstuffs):} You create three days\u8217' worth of jerky and dried fruits that are easily portable and won\u8217't go bad. For each additional success point and unit of foodstuffs, you create another three days\u8217' worth.\par}
