{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b Build Shelter:} You create a shelter that can withstand the current weather for 24 hours. The duration increases by 24 hours for every additional success point you spend.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b Build Raft:} You create a crude raft. It can stay together for 4 hours, although each hour of inclement weather or rapids counts as two hours. The duration increases by 4 hours or every additional success point you spend.\par}
